burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning.actorcritic

Class CritiqueResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learning.actorcritic.CritiqueResult

  • public class CritiqueResult
extends java.lang.Object
    The CritiqueResult class stores the relevant information regarding a critique of behavior. Specifically, it contains the value of the critique, the and the state-action-state tuple that is being critiqued.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
